{"tid":1643221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"施永青指近月集團地產代理業務減少一半以上","createTime":"2019-10-10T04:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T05:39:40.000Z","uid":54373,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"424a57c846daa9d95cf271f5c50c5063ef5610b7","tid":1643221,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:43:00.000Z","msg":"10.10.2019 11:08<br />\n施永青指近月集團地產代理業務減少一半以上 (商台新聞)<br />\n<br />\n中原集團主席施永青在本台節目表示，受反修例事件影響，近月集團地產代理生意減少一半以上，不過公司未有計劃裁員。他指近期商場租金受市況影響會下跌，不過住宅租金仍然穩定，業主對後市仍然樂觀，未有抛售物業情況。<br />\n<br />\n施永青認為本港樓市超越港人購買力，應該分割市場為港人負擔可購買物業。他同意部分私人土地建屋應限制只能向未有物業港人出售，又認為政府應下調農地補地價加快發展，並建議政府將居屋抽籤改為輪候制，以表明會增加供應滿足港人置業需求。"},{"pid":"e9ade0998a8a5db33a6907f4e2066a80c6c25b9b","tid":1643221,"uid":66822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:43:26.000Z","msg":"星期五中環快閃 撐被捕保安<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FoM1jNJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFoM1jNJ.jpg&h=eaa6b73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7onWS7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7onWS7K.jpg&h=4e446c9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5c2649547c1ca663e89ff53e20ecef95dc17a7b","tid":1643221,"uid":329524,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:43:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/underbidding/videos/519124295587506/UzpfSTE2NjgyMDY4Njk6MjQwMTE2Mjc5MDAwMDI3MA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Funderbidding%2Fvideos%2F519124295587506%2FUzpfSTE2NjgyMDY4Njk6MjQwMTE2Mjc5MDAwMDI3MA%2F&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2EmwoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=cc6b92f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/underbidding/videos/519124295587506/UzpfSTE2NjgyMDY4Njk6MjQwMTE2Mjc5MDAwMDI3MA/</a><br />\n哩班究竟係乜野嚟？&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n黑警收埋人地身份証，話人地無出示身份証人.....然後又隋便打&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n而家d狗又玻璃心，又以為自己大L晒，真係好難怪、香港人點解咁憎你地，睇完火都泥🔥<br />\n呢個人係警察咩👮🏿&zwj;♀綠色物體，屌完人老母又話人曱甴法例又唔熟，唔夠人講就